subject: Adjustment of Certain Fees Paid or Payable Under the Special Services (Customs) Regulations for the 2019–2020 to 2025–2026 Fiscal Years Remission Order
precis: Adjustment of Certain Fees Paid or Payable Under the Special Services (Customs) Regulations for the 2019–2020 to 2025–2026 Fiscal Years Remission Order in order to remit any outstanding debts resulting from non-collection of inflation-based adjustments to certain fees charged by the Canada Border Services Agency between April 1, 2019 and March 31, 2026.
